divs: Sighting DetailsIt was Monday afternoon. I went out into the garden to make some pictures with my digital camera of an approaching thunderstorm. I like to picture such events (I���m a hooby photographer). I made some pictures and later on the computer I watched these pictures and suddenly on one I saw a little white dot in the dark clouds. As I zoomed it bigger it appeared to me to be something I never have seen before in that way. As I took the pictures I was looking north. But I haven���t seen anything with my eyes. Only the clouds and the rain of the thunderstorm which was coming closer. Weird... .
